						.row
							.col-md-12.text-center
								p.crp-biotxt The android ape dreamed of running outside of his cage. After being forcably digitized by an amoral cosmetics company, an innocent bonobo became ROBONOBO - weaponized robot ape for hire. He was scared. His life was so violent. Until the day he was introduced to the crime lord KNOX. KNOX opened the door of ROBONOBO's cage and him home to become his faithful son. It was a good life for a young chimp but Robo still couldn't quite shake the feeling that something was very wrong.

								p.crp-biotxt Strapped up with rockets, machine guns, bombs and battle armor, cybernetic ape ROBONOBO is a founding member of KNOX's criminal organization. Childish and aloof, ROBONOBO is far more likely to play video games or eat cereal than rob a bank. Somewhere along the line, Robo's personality began to change. As his intelligence began to increase, ROBO became withdrawn and militant. Torn between his loyalty to KNOX and his own traumatic memories, ROBONOBO's inner turmoil is surfacing in an unpredicatable and violent way.
